      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BATTLE SPEED (6) took the sit on the lead from an outside box but levelled up and drew clear to score (19.42) at this track in a Grade 5 over 340m. Won at his only start from this draw. Looks a key chance if runs up to latest figure. ALBATROSS (2) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (19.07) from Box 1 at Richmond. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Expected to be in this for a long way. REALLY SAVAGE (3) found trouble in the run at this course and distance last time and fell. Has the ability and can atone with the right run. TURBO MISS (1) was a surprise last-start placegetter worth considering.",
